		<descript>
			<abstract>Hydrology representing major hydrologic features digitized from 1:24,000-scale USGS topographic maps. This is selected hydrologic features, not all hydrologic features found on the USGS topographic maps.</abstract>
			<purpose>
This data is used for illustrative and modeling purposes to meet the needs of the U.S. Bureau of Reclamation.

This database is not intended to be used as a land survey or representation of land for conveyance or tax purposes. The database is available to all users that may require this information.
</purpose>
			<supplinf> This dataset has been reformatted by the
    California Spatial Information Library URL:http://gis.ca.gov.
    Processing methodology is described under the Data Quality section.</supplinf>
		</descript>
